msgid ""
"Run batch and Flink-style continuous SQL over Klein for Ray DataStreams "
"and define connectors with Table DDL."
msgstr "在 Klein for Ray DataStream 上运行批处理和 Flink 风格的持续 SQL，并使用 Table DDL 定义连接器。"

msgid "Ray-native SQL and Table connectors"
msgstr "Ray 原生 SQL 与 Table 连接器"

msgid ""
"Klein SQL uses one SQLGlot AST with two Ray-native execution backends. "
"Bounded batch queries lower to lazy Ray Dataset operations. Continuous "
"queries lower to Klein operators with managed keyed state, checkpoints, "
"key groups, and changelog output. SQLGlot is the parser, not an execution"
" engine, and Klein does not embed DuckDB."
msgstr ""
"Klein SQL 使用同一棵 SQLGlot AST，并提供两个 Ray 原生执行后端。有界批查询下沉为惰性 Ray Dataset "
"操作；持续查询下沉为带托管键控状态、检查点、键组和变更日志输出的 Klein 算子。SQLGlot 是解析器而非执行引擎，Klein 也没有嵌入 "
"DuckDB。"

msgid "Choose a SQL entry point"
msgstr "选择 SQL 入口"

msgid "Entry point"
msgstr "入口"

msgid "Use it for"
msgstr "适用场景"

msgid "Catalog lifetime"
msgstr "Catalog 生命周期"

msgid "`ray.klein.sql(query, tables=...)`"
msgstr "`ray.klein.sql(query, tables=...)`"

msgid "A one-off query with explicit or caller-scope bindings."
msgstr "使用显式绑定或调用方作用域绑定的一次性查询。"

msgid "One query"
msgstr "单次查询"

msgid "`stream.sql(query)`"
msgstr "`stream.sql(query)`"

msgid "A query rooted at one stream, bound as `self` by default."
msgstr "以一条流为根的查询，默认将该流绑定为 `self`。"

msgid "The stream context's persistent session"
msgstr "流上下文的持久 session"

msgid "`ray.klein.execute_sql(statement)`"
msgstr "`ray.klein.execute_sql(statement)`"

msgid "`SELECT`, Table DDL, and `INSERT INTO`."
msgstr "`SELECT`、Table DDL 和 `INSERT INTO`。"

msgid "The current pipeline's persistent session"
msgstr "当前管道的持久 session"

msgid ""
"Use `ray.klein.execute_sql()` for a catalog workflow. The top-level "
"`ray.klein.sql()` creates a fresh session for its one query, so it does "
"not see tables previously created through `execute_sql()`. It does inherit "
"scalar functions registered on the current context."
msgstr ""
"在 catalog 工作流中使用 `ray.klein.execute_sql()`。顶层 `ray.klein.sql()` 会为单次查询创建全新 "
"session，因此无法看到此前通过 `execute_sql()` 创建的表，但会继承当前上下文中注册的标量函数。"

msgid "Query DataStreams from Python"
msgstr "从 Python 查询 DataStream"

msgid ""
"The top-level `sql` function discovers named `DataStream` variables in "
"the caller's Python scope:"
msgstr "顶层 `sql` 函数会在调用方的 Python 作用域中发现具名 `DataStream` 变量："

msgid "Explicit bindings are preferable in library code:"
msgstr "在库代码中，最好使用显式绑定："

msgid ""
"For reusable catalog state, `ray.klein.execute_sql()` keeps temporary "
"tables in the current pipeline session. A stream can use the conventional"
" `self` relation:"
msgstr "为了复用 catalog 状态，`ray.klein.execute_sql()` 会在当前管道 session 中保留临时表。数据流可以使用约定的 `self` 关系："

msgid "Register Python scalar functions"
msgstr "注册 Python 标量函数"

msgid ""
"Klein SQL scalar functions use ordinary Python values and do not expose a Ray "
"Data expression contract. Register a function, then call it from SQL with an "
"unquoted, case-insensitive name:"
msgstr ""
"Klein SQL 标量函数使用普通 Python 值，不暴露 Ray Data 表达式契约。请先注册函数，"
"再在 SQL 中通过不带引号且不区分大小写的名称调用它："

msgid ""
"For an explicitly isolated `KleinContext`, register through "
"`context.sql_session.register_scalar_function()` instead."
msgstr ""
"对于显式隔离的 `KleinContext`，请改用 "
"`context.sql_session.register_scalar_function()` 注册。"

msgid ""
"For a one-off `ray.klein.sql()` query, pass query-local bindings. They override "
"same-named session functions without changing the session:"
msgstr ""
"对于一次性的 `ray.klein.sql()` 查询，请传入查询本地绑定。它们会覆盖同名会话函数，"
"但不会修改会话本身："

msgid ""
"Arguments are evaluated with SQL semantics and passed as Python scalars. SQL "
"`NULL` is passed as `None`; the function decides whether to propagate or replace "
"it. Functions work in projections, predicates, grouping expressions, and built-in "
"aggregate inputs. Registration validates the name and callable; query planning "
"validates call arity and rejects unknown functions before workers run. Built-in "
"SQL/Klein function names cannot be replaced."
msgstr ""
"参数会按 SQL 语义求值并作为 Python 标量传入。SQL `NULL` 会作为 `None` 传入；函数自行决定"
"传播还是替换它。函数可用于投影、谓词、分组表达式和内置聚合输入。注册会验证名称和可调用性；"
"查询规划会验证调用参数数量，并在 worker 运行前拒绝未知函数。内置 SQL/Klein 函数名称不可替换。"

msgid ""
"The function and its closure are serialized with the query graph. Install its "
"dependencies on every worker and treat it as trusted application code. Scalar "
"functions are synchronous, share the enclosing SQL operator's resources, and run "
"row by row. For model initialization, GPU allocation, vectorized inference, "
"external-service concurrency, or explicit batching, use `map_batches()` (or an "
"async `map`) before SQL and query the produced columns. Aggregate UDFs are not "
"supported. In streaming changelog or recoverable queries, functions must also be "
"deterministic and side-effect-free: the same arguments must always produce the "
"same result so retractions remain correct, and retries may invoke a function more "
"than once. Materialize nondeterministic or external results before SQL."
msgstr ""
"函数及其闭包会随查询图一起序列化。请在每个 worker 上安装其依赖，并将其视为受信任的应用代码。"
"标量函数必须同步执行，共享所在 SQL 算子的资源，并逐行运行。若需要模型初始化、GPU 分配、"
"向量化推理、外部服务并发或显式批处理，请在 SQL 之前使用 `map_batches()`（或异步 `map`），"
"再查询生成的列。暂不支持聚合 UDF。在流式 changelog 或可恢复查询中，函数还必须确定且无副作用："
"相同参数必须始终生成相同结果，以保证撤回正确；重试也可能多次调用函数。请在 SQL 之前物化非确定性"
"或外部结果。"

msgid "Run a continuous query"
msgstr "运行持续查询"

msgid ""
"Streaming SQL follows Flink's [dynamic "
"table](https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-"
"stable/docs/dev/table/concepts/dynamic_tables/) model. An ordinary "
"mapping is an `INSERT` row. Updating queries emit `ChangelogRow` values "
"whose `row_kind` is `+I`, `-U`, `+U`, or `-D`."
msgstr ""
"流式 SQL 遵循 Flink 的[动态表](https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-"
"stable/docs/dev/table/concepts/dynamic_tables/)模型。普通映射是一个 `INSERT` "
"行。更新型查询发出 `ChangelogRow` 值，其 `row_kind` 为 `+I`、`-U`、`+U` 或 `-D`。"

msgid ""
"The materialized result after every change is equivalent to the same SQL "
"query over the current input snapshot. The example emits `+I` for `Ada = "
"10`, then `-U` for the old row and `+U` for `Ada = 25`. Append-only "
"filters and projections preserve the incoming row kind. Regular equality "
"joins keep both inputs in checkpointed state and emit insert/delete "
"changes for matching rows."
msgstr ""
"每次变更后的物化结果，等同于在当前输入快照上执行相同 SQL 查询。示例为 `Ada = 10` 发出 `+I`，随后为旧行发出 `-U`，并为 "
"`Ada = 25` 发出 "
"`+U`。仅追加的过滤和投影会保留传入的行种类。常规等值连接会将两侧输入保存在带检查点的状态中，并为匹配行发出插入/删除变更。"

msgid ""
"Use a `STATE_TTL` hint to bound idle regular-join or aggregation state, "
"with the same warning as Flink: expiring state can make later results "
"incomplete."
msgstr "使用 `STATE_TTL` hint 限制空闲常规连接或聚合状态，同时须注意与 Flink 相同的警告：状态过期可能使后续结果不完整。"

msgid ""
"Set a pipeline default with `table.exec.state.ttl=1h` or "
"`RAY_KLEIN_TABLE_EXEC_STATE_TTL=1h`. A hint takes precedence for its "
"table alias. State snapshots use the configured Klein backend and the Ray"
" Object Store checkpoint cache, so recovery and key-group rescaling use "
"the same path as native stateful operators."
msgstr ""
"使用 `table.exec.state.ttl=1h` 或 `RAY_KLEIN_TABLE_EXEC_STATE_TTL=1h` "
"设置管道默认值。对于其表别名，hint 具有更高优先级。状态快照使用已配置的 Klein 后端和 Ray Object Store "
"检查点缓存，因此恢复和键组扩缩容与原生有状态算子使用相同路径。"

msgid ""
"Flink does not allow an arbitrary global sort over an unbounded table. "
"Klein therefore rejects streaming `ORDER BY` unless it is paired with "
"`LIMIT`; time-attribute ordering is not implemented yet. `ORDER BY ... "
"LIMIT n` is planned as a continuously maintained Top-N table and emits "
"insert/delete changes when rows enter or leave the result."
msgstr ""
"Flink 不允许对无界表进行任意全局排序。因此，除非与 `LIMIT` 配对，否则 Klein 会拒绝流式 `ORDER "
"BY`；时间属性排序尚未实现。`ORDER BY ... LIMIT n` 会被规划为持续维护的 Top-N "
"表，并在行进入或离开结果时发出插入/删除变更。"

msgid ""
"Regular joins, non-windowed aggregates, and Top-N are stateful. Without a"
" TTL, their state can grow for the lifetime of an unbounded input. A "
"global Top-N is also a single keyed partition, so increasing unrelated "
"operator parallelism does not remove that bottleneck."
msgstr ""
"常规连接、非窗口聚合和 Top-N 都是有状态操作。如果没有 TTL，其状态可能在无界输入的整个生命周期中持续增长。全局 Top-N "
"还是单个键控分区，因此增加无关算子的并行度无法消除这一瓶颈。"

msgid "Define connectors with Flink-style Table DDL"
msgstr "使用 Flink 风格的 Table DDL 定义连接器"

msgid ""
"Catalog tables follow Flink Table DDL: the schema is logical metadata and"
" the `WITH` map selects and configures a connector factory. Creating a "
"table does not open files, create Kafka consumers, or launch Ray tasks."
msgstr ""
"Catalog 表遵循 Flink Table DDL：schema 是逻辑元数据，`WITH` "
"映射用于选择和配置连接器工厂。创建表不会打开文件、创建 Kafka consumer 或启动 Ray 任务。"

msgid ""
"In streaming mode, the filesystem sink is checkpoint-transactional. Part "
"files remain below a hidden `.klein-staging` path until their committable"
" is present in durable checkpoint metadata, then the coordinator "
"publishes them idempotently. Flink-style options such as "
"`sink.parallelism`, `sink.rolling-policy.file-size`, `sink.rolling-policy"
".rollover-interval`, and `sink.rolling-policy.inactivity-interval` "
"configure the native sink. See the [Filesystem "
"connector](connectors/filesystem.md) for the full lifecycle and option "
"table."
msgstr ""
"在流式模式下，文件系统 sink 具备检查点事务性。分片文件会保留在隐藏的 `.klein-staging` "
"路径下，直到其可提交项出现在持久检查点元数据中，随后协调器以幂等方式发布这些文件。`sink.parallelism`、`sink"
".rolling-policy.file-size`、`sink.rolling-policy.rollover-interval` 和 "
"`sink.rolling-policy.inactivity-interval` 等 Flink 风格选项用于配置原生 "
"sink。完整生命周期和选项表请参阅[文件系统连接器](connectors/filesystem.md)。"

msgid ""
"Built-in connector identifiers are `filesystem`, `kafka`, and `print`. "
"The dedicated [connector catalog](connectors/index.md) lists their "
"complete option sets, defaults, data shapes, and delivery guarantees. "
"Applications can implement `TableFactory` and register it with "
"`SQLSession.register_table_factory()`. A factory validates table options "
"at `CREATE TABLE` time and binds a source or sink only when the table is "
"read or used by `INSERT INTO`. Third-party packages can publish factories"
" through the `ray.klein.table_factories` Python entry-point group."
msgstr ""
"内置连接器标识符为 `filesystem`、`kafka` 和 "
"`print`。专门的[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)列出了完整选项集、默认值、数据形态和交付保证。应用可以实现 "
"`TableFactory`，并通过 `SQLSession.register_table_factory()` 注册。工厂在 `CREATE "
"TABLE` 时验证表选项，并且只在读取表或通过 `INSERT INTO` 使用表时才绑定源或 sink。第三方软件包可通过 "
"`ray.klein.table_factories` Python 入口点组发布工厂。"

msgid ""
"Kafka is deliberately not a second Klein-specific API. Its table options "
"and Python methods reuse Ray Data 2.56 names: `topics`, "
"`bootstrap_servers`, `trigger`, `start_offset`, `end_offset`, "
"`consumer_config`, resource options, and `timeout_ms` for reads; `topic`,"
" `key_field`, serializers, `producer_config`, `ray_remote_args`, and "
"`concurrency` for writes. Complex option values use JSON strings."
msgstr ""
"Kafka 有意不提供另一套 Klein 专用 API。其表选项和 Python 方法复用 Ray Data 2.56 命名：读取使用 "
"`topics`、`bootstrap_servers`、`trigger`、`start_offset`、`end_offset`、`consumer_config`、资源选项和"
" `timeout_ms`；写入使用 "
"`topic`、`key_field`、serializer、`producer_config`、`ray_remote_args` 和 "
"`concurrency`。复杂选项值使用 JSON 字符串。"

msgid ""
"Message encodings remain formats owned by the physical connector. For "
"example, Canal CDC uses `'connector'='kafka'`, `'format'='canal-json'`, "
"with `canal-json.*` format options; it is not registered as a separate "
"connector."
msgstr ""
"消息编码仍是物理连接器所拥有的格式。例如，Canal CDC 使用 `'connector'='kafka'`、`'format'='canal-"
"json'` 和 `canal-json.*` 格式选项；它不会注册为独立连接器。"

msgid ""
"The connector also validates the read-side `concurrency`, "
"`partition_discovery_interval_ms`, and `max_batch_size` options used by "
"the Python continuous source. A Kafka table with `'trigger' = "
"'continuous'` selects the streaming SQL planner automatically."
msgstr ""
"连接器还会验证 Python 持续源使用的读取端 `concurrency`、`partition_discovery_interval_ms` "
"和 `max_batch_size` 选项。设置 `'trigger' = 'continuous'` 的 Kafka 表会自动选择流式 SQL "
"planner。"

msgid "How does SQL execute?"
msgstr "SQL 如何执行？"

msgid "The batch lowering boundary is:"
msgstr "批处理下沉边界如下："

msgid ""
"Projection and predicates become Ray row transforms; equi-joins use "
"`Dataset.join`; grouping uses `GroupedData.aggregate`; ordering and "
"limits use their native Dataset operators. Data stays partitioned in "
"Ray's Object Store, so there is no single-node SQL task or driver-side "
"`take_all()` boundary."
msgstr ""
"投影和谓词变为 Ray 行转换；等值连接使用 `Dataset.join`；分组使用 "
"`GroupedData.aggregate`；排序和限制使用各自的原生 Dataset 算子。数据在 Ray 的 Object Store "
"中保持分区，因此不存在单节点 SQL 任务或 driver 端 `take_all()` 边界。"

msgid "The streaming lowering boundary is:"
msgstr "流式下沉边界如下："

msgid "The two planners intentionally have different feature sets:"
msgstr "两个 planner 有意采用不同的功能集："

