msgid "SQL window syntax and time-attribute DDL"
msgstr "SQL 窗口语法和时间属性 DDL"

msgid ""
"Join `ON` conditions are conjunctions of equality predicates between "
"qualified left and right columns; `USING` is also supported. Unsupported "
"forms raise `SQLQueryError` instead of silently changing semantics. All "
"inputs must belong to the same Klein pipeline."
msgstr ""
"连接的 `ON` 条件是限定左右列之间等值谓词的合取，也支持 `USING`。不受支持的形式会引发 "
"`SQLQueryError`，而不会静默更改语义。所有输入必须属于同一个 Klein 管道。"

msgid ""
"Bounded SQL translates compatible SQLGlot nodes to native Ray 2.56 "
"expression ASTs before falling back to Klein's row evaluator. This covers"
" columns, literals, arithmetic/comparison/boolean/null predicates, casts,"
" lower/upper, common numeric functions, `RANDOM([seed])`, `UUID()`, and "
"`MONOTONICALLY_INCREASING_ID()`. The I/O form `DOWNLOAD(uri_column)` is "
"supported as a standalone projection or aggregate input, for example:"
msgstr ""
"有界 SQL 会先将兼容的 SQLGlot 节点转换为原生 Ray 2.56 表达式 AST，再回退到 Klein "
"的行求值器。支持范围包括列、字面量、算术/比较/布尔/null "
"谓词、类型转换、lower/upper、常用数值函数、`RANDOM([seed])`、`UUID()` 和 "
"`MONOTONICALLY_INCREASING_ID()`。I/O 形式 `DOWNLOAD(uri_column)` "
"可用作独立投影或聚合输入，例如："

msgid ""
"In batch mode, `DOWNLOAD` lowers to Ray Data's dedicated URI download "
"operator. In streaming mode, Klein uses a bounded, order-preserving "
"asynchronous operator so downloads do not block the task actor and a full"
" in-flight window propagates backpressure. Composing `DOWNLOAD` inside "
"another scalar expression or using it as a predicate is rejected. "
"`RANDOM([seed])`, `UUID()`, and `MONOTONICALLY_INCREASING_ID()` are task-"
"local streaming expressions and work in projections, predicates, "
"grouping, and aggregate inputs where their SQL types are valid."
msgstr ""
"在批处理模式下，`DOWNLOAD` 下沉为 Ray Data 专用 URI 下载算子。在流式模式下，Klein "
"使用有界、保序的异步算子，使下载不会阻塞任务 actor，并在在途窗口已满时传播背压。系统会拒绝在其他标量表达式中组合 `DOWNLOAD` "
"或将其用作谓词。`RANDOM([seed])`、`UUID()` 和 `MONOTONICALLY_INCREASING_ID()` "
"是任务本地流式表达式，只要 SQL 类型有效，就可用于投影、谓词、分组和聚合输入。"

msgid ""
"Data definition language (DDL) and data manipulation language (DML) "
"support `CREATE [TEMPORARY] TABLE`, `DROP TABLE`, and `INSERT INTO ... "
"SELECT`. Catalog-qualified names, computed columns, watermarks, "
"partitions, and `INSERT` target-column lists are reserved for later "
"planner iterations."
msgstr ""
"数据定义语言 (DDL) 和数据操作语言 (DML) 支持 `CREATE [TEMPORARY] TABLE`、`DROP TABLE` 和 "
"`INSERT INTO ... SELECT`。Catalog 限定名称、计算列、水位线、分区和 `INSERT` 目标列列表留待后续 "
"planner 迭代支持。"

msgid "Distinguish queries from the database sink"
msgstr "区分查询与数据库 sink"

msgid ""
"`DataStream.write_sql()` writes rows through a Python DB-API connection; "
"it is not a `connector='sql'` Table factory. In batch mode it delegates "
"to Ray Data. In streaming mode each sink subtask owns a connection and "
"flushes buffered `executemany` calls when 128 rows accumulate, at "
"checkpoints, and at close. Its delivery guarantee is at-least-once, so "
"use idempotent statements, a unique key, or a database-native upsert. See"
" [Delivery semantics](delivery-semantics.md) before using it in a "
"recoverable pipeline."
msgstr ""
"`DataStream.write_sql()` 通过 Python DB-API 连接写入行；它不是 `connector='sql'` "
"Table 工厂。在批处理模式下，它委托给 Ray Data。在流式模式下，每个 sink 子任务拥有一个连接，并在累计 128 "
"行、建立检查点和关闭时刷新已缓冲的 `executemany` 调用。其交付保证为至少一次，因此请使用幂等语句、唯一键或数据库原生 "
"upsert。将其用于可恢复管道前，请参阅[交付语义](delivery-semantics.md)。"

